{"tid":1482094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請考慮設立平台幫助前線雜項開支","createTime":"2019-08-18T03:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T03:53:18.000Z","uid":53331,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"029e3a4d9cbda32e907710f2cad5baff48e77367","tid":1482094,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:35:55.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有冇發現日以繼夜嘅發夢嘅雜項開支期實好驚人，特別係對一眾學生來講根本好難負擔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個問題已經慢慢顯現岀來<br />\n<br />\n所以有兩個諗法<br />\n設立基金集中處理發夢者成本申請<br />\n設立每區tg group 以分區幫助有需要人士<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學生依家根本就應該係享受暑假 係一個快樂嘅時間 點解佢地比大人行得更前之外重要令到佢地連生活都有困難<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47af41fa0214ad8d249db71d4713184cb5b3c18","tid":1482094,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:45:48.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n818維園見！所有聽日去嘅人都同我入一入嚟！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1480894\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1480894</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"970a9a7572038ec1840f5171fcb5354d2c9dcfc4","tid":1482094,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:46:15.000Z","msg":"818維園見"},{"pid":"58f6fe0a9ceec39cc0b965e03b8bf3a73b568a27","tid":1482094,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:46:26.000Z","msg":"721 811<br />\n818維園見"},{"pid":"a71837f16f11671155e89dfe969eb8edc58f9d23","tid":1482094,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:46:38.000Z","msg":"721 811<br />\n818維園見"},{"pid":"296491b7ac205bcc062e1408192865995e8febd4","tid":1482094,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:51:33.000Z","msg":"721 811<br />\n818維園見<br />\n<br /